flowchart LR
    A[Staff uploads photo/PDF] --> B[Local preprocessing: deskew, denoise, enhance]
    B --> C[EasyOCR extracts text and word boxes]
    C --> D[Handwriting layer]
    D --> D1[Current: EasyOCR baseline]
    D --> D2[Upgrade: Qwen2.5-VL via MLX-VLM]
    D --> D3[Upgrade: PaddleOCR PP-OCRv5]
    D1 --> E[Profile-aware redaction]
    D2 --> E
    D3 --> E
    E --> F[Opaque image masks + redacted text]
    F --> G[Translation if non-English]
    G --> H[Classify category + route department]
    H --> I[Urgency, sentiment, safeguarding flags]
    I --> J[Audit log + outputs: image, TXT, JSON, DOCX]
    J --> K[Staff approve or send to review]
